OL,3,C70% of adults without a licence say
OL,4,Clearning to drive is unaffordable
OL,6,FSome seven in 10 British adults
OL,7,Fwithout a full driving licence say
OL,8,Flearning to drive is currently
OL,9,Funaffordable, according to a survey.
OL,11,FThe figure is even higher among
OL,12,Fyounger people, with 76% of 18 to 29-
OL,13,Fyear-olds without a licence saying
OL,14,Fdriving lessons are financially out of
OL,15,Freach, the poll for car insurer Prima
OL,16,Ffound.
OL,18,FOverall, 38% said the cost of driving
OL,19,Flessons was the biggest deterrent to
OL,20,Flearning to drive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
