OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772935393
OL,3,C70% of adults without a licence say
OL,4,Clearning to drive is unaffordable
OL,6,FSome 32% were put off by the price of
OL,7,Fbuying a car and 15% said the cost of
OL,8,Fcar insurance was the main barrier to
OL,9,Flearning to drive.
OL,11,FAlmost half (45%) said they would
OL,12,Fconsider learning to drive if it
OL,13,Fbecame significantly cheaper.
OL,15,FNick Ielpo, UK country manager at
OL,16,FPrima, said: "For a growing number of
OL,17,Fpeople, driving is no longer a symbol
OL,18,Fof freedom ` it's a financial stretch
OL,19,Ftoo far.
OL,26,@xD@NOU
