OL,3,C70% of adults without a licence say
OL,4,Clearning to drive is unaffordable
OL,6,F"Between lessons, buying a car and
OL,7,Finsuring it, the upfront and ongoing
OL,8,Fcosts are pricing many people out
OL,9,Fbefore they even start."
OL,11,FFind Out Now surveyed 1,134 adults who
OL,12,Fdo not hold a full driving licence
OL,13,Fbetween January 21 and 23.
